  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of EVT 101 in Treatment-Resistant Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 4-Week, Randomized, Double-Blind, Parallel-Group, Placebo-Controlled Study to Investigate the Safety and Efficacy of EVT 101 as Monotherapy in Patients With Treatment-Resistant Major Depression</official_title>
  <sponsors>
