  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a 4-week, randomized, double-blind, parallel-group, placebo-controlled
      monotherapy study in patients with treatment-resistant major depression. After confirmation
      of treatment-resistance in a prospective treatment period with citalopram, each patient will
      be treated with either EVT 101 once daily or placebo for 28 consecutive days.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
